   note = {* For the interspecific range of hydraulic traits in the previously published studies, the range of variation of P50 was –3.64 MPa (–0.56 to –4.2 MPa); in this study, the intraspecific range of P50 for S. micranthum was –3.54 MPa (–0.14 to –3.68 MPa, i.e. 97% of the interspecific range), and for P. hebetatum it was –2.76 MPa (–0.14 to –2.9 MPa, 76% of the interspecific range).},
